   Example usage:

   >>> print dirac.checkSites()
   {'OK': True, 'Value': {'AllowedSites':['<Site>',...],'BannedSites':[]}

   @param printOutput: Optional flag to print result
   @type printOutput: boolean
   @return: S_OK,S_ERROR

